{"tid":287382,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"又打錯字啦！吳業坤話好想「釣」人食飯","createTime":"2017-06-17T11:30:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-18T08:56:00.000Z","uid":35964,"like":1,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c4bff0e8c39b3c09ebb1c669c11768e9ef357f33","tid":287382,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T11:30:58.000Z","msg":"歌手吳業坤一向鍾意喺社交網同網民互動，但係唔知佢有意定唔小心喇，有好多次打錯字嘅經驗㖭！今日佢又喺社交網發文，話「好想釣人食飯」，網民就反問佢其係係咪好想「約」人食飯呀？其實數吓數吓，吳業坤都有好多次類次事件，好似佢最經典嘅「食好西」啦、「訂咗兩隻WIFE（WIFI）」、「有無D停車場係女平」，真係好唔小心囉！網民都話好期待吳業坤有新經典潮語出現呀！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170616/photo/bkn-20170616224337880-0616_00862_001_02b.jpg?20170616230146\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170616%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170616224337880-0616_00862_001_02b.jpg%3F20170616230146&h=ad311c37&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"03be3c1df045c3d592ac4226ac59e3b61dbb8958","tid":287382,"uid":48285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T11:33:46.000Z","msg":"其實條友文盲嚟"},{"pid":"7446595936a344b1c2fa3d2b78590ea4ed9dd6f8","tid":287382,"uid":22024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T11:34:29.000Z","msg":"假膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc8deceeef4b98b59888a20b2d63ecf2b1eeea15","tid":287382,"uid":80814,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T11:34:29.000Z","msg":"同一招用太多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"658e7813f5b50fc9dc489761ae971d0d5f1b0625","tid":287382,"uid":106149,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T11:35:14.000Z","msg":"呢條撚樣 扮傻 咁多次 仲會有人信？"},{"pid":"71ac2f7f4e5c4fe5d4cd0fbe4c7f69f17ae3db4a","tid":287382,"uid":20460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T11:38:17.000Z","msg":"第一次就好玩，第二次就on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d380536151707